k-hole mergers, resolvability is not a limiting criteria\nfor these modes. We emphasize that the measurability of the $l=2, m=1$ mode is\nnot impeded by the resolvability criterion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Jul 2016 19:10:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 28 Jan 2017 19:04:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-31"}
