ucture on the substrate. In particular, we show how\nprestructure stripes parallel to the transfer direction lead to the formation\nof bent stripes in the surfactant coverage after transfer and present similar\nexperimental results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Jul 2016 14:27:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 14 Dec 2016 13:10:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-15"}
